```plantuml
@startuml gcba-iris_iris
skinparam rectangle {
  BackgroundColor #ffffff
  BorderColor black
  Style roundrect
}
left to right direction

actor User

rectangle "CLI" as CLI #aliceblue
rectangle "Main Entry Point\n(index.js)" as MainEntry #lightyellow

rectangle "Dispatcher" as Dispatcher #lightsteelblue {
}

rectangle "Dock" as Dock #palegreen
rectangle "Handler" as Handler #thistle
rectangle "Hook" as Hook #wheat

rectangle "Thread Pool" as ThreadPool #mistyrose

rectangle "Logger" as Logger #lightgray

' ========== Connections ==========
User --> CLI : Initialize Iris / Execute Command

CLI --> MainEntry : Run iris.js

MainEntry --> Dispatcher : Initialize / Register Flows

Dock --> Dispatcher : Send parsed data objects

Dispatcher --> Hook : Execute input hooks

Dispatcher --> Handler : Route data for processing

Handler --> Dispatcher : Send response back

Dispatcher --> Hook : Execute output hooks

Dispatcher --> ThreadPool : Assign job for concurrent execution

ThreadPool --> Dispatcher : Execute data flows in parallel

MainEntry --> Logger : Log information and errors

@enduml
```